  <refsect1>
     <title>Description</title>
     <para>The <link linkend="class-ossoabookgroupmodel">
     <classname>abook.GroupModel</classname></link>
     is a model that lists user-defined groups (see
     <link linkend="class-ossoabookgroup"><classname>abook.Group</classname></link>).
     Additional groups can be added using the
     <link linkend="method-ossoabookgroupmodel--add-group"><methodname>abook.GroupModel.add_group()</methodname></link>
     method.</para>
  </refsect1>
